I got an issue with people coming in Help expecting everyone to do their thinking FOR them... I dont mind helping, but be damned if you think I'm babysitting you... You want someone to hold your hand, Keep Looking...


If you're broke, I'm not giving you money... I'm teaching you how to make a kick-ass resume. I will show you how to find your own answers. If you dont like the answer I give, Just say, "Thanks, but Ill find another way", I will gladly step aside, and let you find your own groove...


Eve Rules :-

1: Highsec is not safe. Lowsec is not safe. Nullsec is not safe. Never assume anything...
2: Trust NO-ONE!
3: Never fly anything (or with anything in cargo) you can't afford to lose.
4: NEVER mix tank. You become "average" at either and die a lot
5: NEVER mix guns. same reason

8: Right click, SHOW INFO are your best friends

Goonswarm Federation's largest member Corporation where Eve's most knowledgeable veterans help teach pilots to fly. New players come here to learn from the best, old players come here to revitalize their Eve experience. KarmaFleet has an abundance of unique supportive services available only to our pilots like Corp level SRP(on top of Alliance SRP), ISK payouts to our FCs, and a PLEX for PVP program that rewards our pilots. 98366310.description:
In this vast universe, there are all sorts of creatures. Among those are those that have lost their way, they forgot what it means to be a human. The Amarr, wanting to enslave others, justifying it all through their beliefs. The Caldari, focusing on their profits and treating others not as humans, but as assets; a corporate enslavement. These people cannot be allowed to expand. We must bring the universe into a more unionized condition. With the help of our allies, the Minmatar, we will focus our efforts into aiding the people of Caldari. We shall go into their space, capture it, and free the people; let them know there is a better system that allows them to have a voice. A system that makes them human.
This corporation is a corporation designed to take in all sorts of players, regardless of factions, race, and real life details such as religion, gender, etc., focused on freeing the people in Caldari control, at any cost, including our own losses of a couple of clones. With every loss, we come back smarter and stronger. We WILL unite the peoples of New Eden, but will only do so if we are united as one in this vast universe
We simply want to have the ability to grow stronger and blow up the enemy. Will you be part of our personal conquest, our journey, our vendetta, our goal, victories? Or will you be one of our victims?


We train combat pilots. We also just train pilots in general aspects of the game.


Only rules here is to remain active (if possible, of course), respect each other, and have fun.

What we offer:

-Multiple "HQs" near trading hubs
-An HQ in next to low sec, good for mining and making your own stuff.
-Training in the art of combat and survival.
-More to come!

Our Logo/Emblem:
The Stars: Our union across the stars in this vast universe.
The Golden Winged Creature: The individual representing this emblem with pride.
The Red Blades: The pilots who spill blood everyday through their combat activities.


Happy Gaming and may you join the Union.
